Dialogue: 3,0:00:11.82,0:00:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我是在科幻小说的陪伴下长大的 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.82,0:00:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I grew up on a steady diet of science fiction.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,高中的时候 我每天要搭乘
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,In high school, I took a bus to school
Dialogue: 3,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,一个小时的公交车往返学校 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.82,0:00:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,an hour each way every day.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:21.82,0:00:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,漫长车程中 我总是沉浸在书本里 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.82,0:00:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I was always absorbed in a book,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,那些科幻小说
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,science fiction book,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.82,0:00:28.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,将我的思想带到其他的世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:25.82,0:00:28.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,which took my mind to other worlds,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,以叙事的方式 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and satisfied, in a narrative form,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.82,0:00:37.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,满足了我当时强烈的好奇感 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.82,0:00:37.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,this insatiable sense of curiosity that I had.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,除此之外 我的好奇心也展现在其他方面 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And you know, that curiosity also manifested itself
Dialogue: 3,0:00:40.82,0:00:43.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,每当我不需要上课的时候 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.82,0:00:43.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in the fact that whenever I wasn't in school
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我总会前往树林里 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I was out in the woods,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.82,0:00:49.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,远足和采集“标本” 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.82,0:00:49.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,hiking and taking "samples" --
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,青蛙呀 蛇呀 虫子呀 池水呀 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,frogs and snakes and bugs and pond water --
Dialogue: 3,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,通通带回家中 放到显微镜下研究 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and bringing it back, looking at it under the microscope.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我当时算得上是极品的科学狂人 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You know, I was a real science geek.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.82,0:00:59.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但这一切都是为了尝试了解这个世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.82,0:00:59.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But it was all about trying to understand the world,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:59.82,0:01:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,了解可能的边界 
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.82,0:01:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,understand the limits of possibility.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:03.82,0:01:07.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而我对科幻小说的喜爱
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.82,0:01:07.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And my love of science fiction
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,也是与我周围的世界相呼应的 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,actually seemed mirrored in the world around me,
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因为当时是60年代末期 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,because what was happening, this was in the late '60s,
Dialogue: 3,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,人类开始登月 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,we were going to the moon,
Dialogue: 3,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,开始潜入深海 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,we were exploring the deep oceans.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,雅克.格斯特（法国电影摄影师）将他神奇的视觉特效
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Jacques Cousteau was coming into our living rooms
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,带入我们的生活中 为我们呈现了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,with his amazing specials that showed us
Dialogue: 3,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,之前无法想象的动物 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,animals and places and a wondrous world
Dialogue: 3,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,景观和一个美妙的世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that we could never really have previously imagined.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:28.82,0:01:30.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这一切都似乎和科幻小说之间
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.82,0:01:30.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, that seemed to resonate
Dialogue: 3,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,产生着共鸣 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,with the whole science fiction part of it.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:33.82,0:01:35.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,与此同时 我也是名艺术家 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.82,0:01:35.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I was an artist.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我能绘能画 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I could draw. I could paint.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我也发现因为当时没有电子游戏 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I found that because there weren't video games
Dialogue: 3,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,特效电影的渗入以及现今传媒产业中
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and this saturation of CG movies and all of this
Dialogue: 3,0:01:44.82,0:01:47.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,大量的图像化 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.82,0:01:47.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,imagery in the media landscape,
Dialogue: 3,0:01:47.82,0:01:49.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我不得不在我的头脑中来创造这些图像 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.82,0:01:49.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I had to create these images in my head.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,相信大家小时候都和我一样 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You know, we all did, as kids having to
Dialogue: 3,0:01:51.82,0:01:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在读书的时候 往往会在我们大脑中
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.82,0:01:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,read a book, and through the author's description,
Dialogue: 3,0:01:54.82,0:01:58.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,把作者所描述的东西向电影一样播放 
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.82,0:01:58.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,put something on the movie screen in our heads.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而我对此的回应则是描绘
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And so, my response to this was to paint, to draw
Dialogue: 3,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,外星生物 外星世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,alien creatures, alien worlds,
Dialogue: 3,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,机器人 宇宙飞船 等等 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,robots, spaceships, all that stuff.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我躲在教科书后面涂鸦的行径
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I was endlessly getting busted in math class
Dialogue: 3,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,总是被数学老师给逮个正着 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,doodling behind the textbook.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,正因此 我不得不为我的创造力
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,That was -- the creativity
Dialogue: 3,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,寻求其他的宣泄途径 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,had to find its outlet somehow.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,有趣的是 雅克.格斯特的影片令我惊喜地发现
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And an interesting thing happened: The Jacques Cousteau shows
Dialogue: 3,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,原来在这个地球上
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,actually got me very excited about the fact that there was
Dialogue: 3,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,就存在着一个外星世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,an alien world right here on Earth.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我也许无法真的在有生之年
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I might not really go to an alien world
Dialogue: 3,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,乘坐宇宙飞船前往外星世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,on a spaceship someday --
Dialogue: 3,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这听起来太不着边际了 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that seemed pretty darn unlikely.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但这个地球上确实存在着一个
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But that was a world I could really go to,
Dialogue: 3,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我真的可以前往的世界——
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,right here on Earth, that was as rich and exotic
Dialogue: 3,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,富饶而奇异 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,as anything that I had imagined
Dialogue: 3,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,拥有着我通过书本所幻想的一切 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,from reading these books.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:43.82,0:02:45.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因此在我15岁的那一年 我决定成为一名
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.82,0:02:45.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, I decided I was going to become a scuba diver
Dialogue: 3,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,潜水员 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,at the age of 15.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,不过唯一的问题是 我当时
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And the only problem with that was that I lived
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,住在加拿大的一个小村庄里 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in a little village in Canada,
Dialogue: 3,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,最近的海也要600英里远 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,600 miles from the nearest ocean.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但我却没有因此而心灰意冷 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But I didn't let that daunt me.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我反复纠缠我的老爸 直到他在
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I pestered my father until he finally found
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,纽约水牛市为我找到了一个潜水训练班 
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,a scuba class in Buffalo, New York,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,它就在美加边界的另一侧 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,right across the border from where we live.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,就这样 在水牛市刺骨的深冬 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I actually got certified
Dialogue: 3,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在基督教青年会的泳池内 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in a pool at a YMCA in the dead of winter
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我拿到了我的潜水证书 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in Buffalo, New York.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但在随后的两年里 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I didn't see the ocean, a real ocean,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我却不曾亲眼看见过大海 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,for another two years,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,直到我们搬到了加利福尼亚洲 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,until we moved to California.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在那之后
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Since then, in the intervening
Dialogue: 3,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,的40年里 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,40 years,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我在水下度过了大概3000个小时 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I've spent about 3,000 hours underwater,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:26.82,0:03:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,其中500个小时是在潜水器中度过的 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.82,0:03:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and 500 hours of that was in submersibles.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我发现深海之中──
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I've learned that that deep-ocean environment,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,即使是浅海之中──
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and even the shallow oceans,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,充满了令人惊奇的生命 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,are so rich with amazing life
Dialogue: 3,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,远远超出了我们的想象 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that really is beyond our imagination.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,同我们人类狭隘的想象范围相比
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Nature's imagination is so boundless
Dialogue: 3,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,大自然的想象力
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,compared to our own
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是无边无际的 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,meager human imagination.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,直到今日 我潜水时所目睹的一切
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I still, to this day, stand in absolute awe
Dialogue: 3,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,仍令我感到无比惊奇 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of what I see when I make these dives.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我对海洋的热爱
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And my love affair with the ocean is ongoing,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,始终如一 不曾改变 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and just as strong as it ever was.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但当我长大成人 需要择业的时候 
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But when I chose a career as an adult,
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我选择了电影制作 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,it was filmmaking.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在当时看来 这是将我
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And that seemed to be the best way to reconcile
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,讲故事的渴求与创造图象的欲望
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,this urge I had to tell stories
Dialogue: 3,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,合二为一的最好途径 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,with my urges to create images.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在我还是个孩子的时候 我常常画漫画 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I was, as a kid, constantly drawing comic books, and so on.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而电影制作正好将图象和故事结合在一起 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, filmmaking was the way to put pictures and stories
Dialogue: 3,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,理所当然 水到渠成 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,together, and that made sense.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,当然了 我讲的故事都是些科幻故事
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And of course the stories that I chose to tell
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.82,0:04:28.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,《终结者》《异形》和《深渊》  
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.82,0:04:28.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,were science fiction stories: "Terminator," "Aliens" and "The Abyss." 
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在《深渊》中 我将我对深海和潜水的喜爱
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And with "The Abyss," I was putting together my love
Dialogue: 3,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,与电影制作结合到了一起 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of underwater and diving with filmmaking.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:33.82,0:04:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,将两份热忱 合二为一 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.82,0:04:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, you know, merging the two passions.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:36.82,0:04:40.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而《深渊》也带来了另一种启迪 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.82,0:04:40.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Something interesting came out of "The Abyss,"
Dialogue: 3,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,为了更好的呈现
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,which was that to solve a specific narrative
Dialogue: 3,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,影片的叙事模式 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,problem on that film,
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,创造出影片中的液体水生物 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,which was to create this kind of liquid water creature,
Dialogue: 3,0:04:50.82,0:04:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们开始使用电脑动画技术 
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.82,0:04:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,we actually embraced computer generated animation, CG.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:56.82,0:05:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,电影业中的首个
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.82,0:05:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And this resulted in the first soft-surface
Dialogue: 3,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,电脑制作的软表面人物
Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,character, CG animation
Dialogue: 3,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,也因此而诞生 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that was ever in a movie.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,尽管那部电影票房不济 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And even though the film didn't make any money --
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,刚好回本罢了 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,barely broke even, I should say --
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我却因此而目睹了令人惊奇的一幕──
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I witnessed something amazing, which is that the audience,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,全球观众都被影片所呈现的魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,the global audience, was mesmerized
Dialogue: 3,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,深深吸引 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,by this apparent magic.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这就是阿瑟·克拉克定律──
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You know, it's Arthur Clarke's law
Dialogue: 3,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,先进的科技和魔法之间是难以区分的 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而当时观众所目睹的正是这种魔力 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,They were seeing something magical.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这令我感到无比兴奋 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And so that got me very excited.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我当时想到 “天呀 这项技术需要在电影艺术中
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I thought, "Wow, this is something that needs to be embraced
Dialogue: 3,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,大范围推广 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,into the cinematic art."
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以在我的下一部电影《终结者2》中 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, with "Terminator 2," which was my next film,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们将这项技术推上了新的台阶 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,we took that much farther.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.93,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,通过和“工业光魔”的合作 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.93,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Working with ILM,
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.82,0:05:42.13,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,{\an8}工业光魔 (ILM)电影特效公司
Dialogue: 3,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.13,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们创造了影片中那个液体金属家伙  
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.93,0:05:42.13,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,we created the liquid metal dude in that film.  
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而电影的成功与否将取决于这项技术能否奏效  
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,The success hung in the balance on whether that effect would work. 
Dialogue: 3,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,结果它奏效了 我们再次创造了魔法 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it did, and we created magic again,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们再次从观众那里得到了同样的回馈 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and we had the same result with an audience --
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,不过那部电影的票房要稍微好一点 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,although we did make a little more money on that one.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:50.82,0:05:55.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,综合这两次经历 
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.82,0:05:55.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, drawing a line through those two dots
Dialogue: 3,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们意识到
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of experience
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这将是一个全新的世界
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,came to, "This is going to be a whole new world,"
Dialogue: 3,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,一个容许电影艺术者们施展想象力的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,this was a whole new world of creativity
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,全新世界 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,for film artists.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以我和我的好友Stan Winston
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, I started a company with Stan Winston,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,成立了一家公司 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,my good friend Stan Winston,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.82,0:06:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,Stan Winston是当时的知名化妆师和造型师 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.82,0:06:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,who is the premier make-up and creature designer
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.82,0:06:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,公司的名字就叫做"数码领域"（Digital Domain） 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.82,0:06:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,at that time, and it was called Digital Domain.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而公司的理念就是
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And the concept of the company was
Dialogue: 3,0:06:18.82,0:06:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,跳过光学打印机等等的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.82,0:06:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that we would leapfrog past
Dialogue: 3,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,模拟过程 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,the analog processes of optical printers and so on,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,直接转入数码制作 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and we would go right to digital production.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.25,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,事实上我们的确做到了这一点 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.27,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And we actually did that 
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,使得我们在一段时间内占据了先机 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and it gave us a competitive advantage for a while.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但在90年代中叶 我们发现虽然公司的初衷
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But we found ourselves lagging in the mid '90s
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是在生物 人物设计方面有所建树 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in the creature and character design stuff
Dialogue: 3,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但我们在这一方面却是落伍了 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that we had actually founded the company to do.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因此我创作了这个《阿凡达》的作品 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, I wrote this piece called "Avatar,"
Dialogue: 3,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,旨在将视觉效果
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,which was meant to absolutely push the envelope
Dialogue: 3,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,和电脑特效
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of visual effects,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,推向极限 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of CG effects, beyond,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,利用电脑动画制造出
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,with realistic human emotive characters
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,具有真实人类情感的生物 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,generated in CG,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,主要角色将由电脑制作 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and the main characters would all be in CG,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,整个场景将由电脑制作 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and the world would be in CG.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但我却碰了一鼻子灰 
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And the envelope pushed back,
Dialogue: 3,0:07:01.82,0:07:06.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们公司里的人告诉我说
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.82,0:07:06.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and I was told by the folks at my company
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.64,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们在当时的技术条件下 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.64,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that we weren't going to be able
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是无法完成这样的特效的 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,to do this for a while.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.05,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以我将这个想法放置一旁 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.05,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, I shelved it, 
Dialogue: 3,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,转而制作了一部关于大船沉入海底的电影 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and I made this other movie about a big ship that sinks.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.30,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我当时跟电影公司说
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.30,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You know, I went and pitched it to the studio 
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这部电影将会是船上的“罗密欧与朱丽叶” 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,as "'Romeo and Juliet' on a ship:
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,将会是一部史诗般的 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,"It's going to be this epic romance,
Dialogue: 3,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,浪漫激情的电影 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,passionate film."
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但私底下 我的真实动机
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Secretly, what I wanted to do was
Dialogue: 3,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是去拜访一下泰坦尼克的残骸 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dive to the real wreck of "Titanic."
Dialogue: 3,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这才是我制作那部电影的原因 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And that's why I made the movie.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:33.82,0:07:34.87,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我说的是事实 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.82,0:07:34.87,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And that's the truth. 
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,不过电影公司当时是不知情的 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Now, the studio didn't know that.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我说服了他们 我说 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But I convinced them. I said,
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,“我们将潜入船骸 实地取景 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,"We're going to dive to the wreck. We're going to film it for real.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:39.82,0:07:42.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,作为影片的开场 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.82,0:07:42.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,We'll be using it in the opening of the film.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,此事至关重要 极具噱头 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,It will be really important. It will be a great marketing hook."
Dialogue: 3,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,于是我说服了他们投资于一场冒险历程 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I talked them into funding an expedition.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,听起来很疯狂 但这件事归根结底 依旧是关于
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Sounds crazy. But this goes back to that theme
Dialogue: 3,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,如果用你的想像力来创造一个现实 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,about your imagination creating a reality.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,事实上 我们的确在六个月后创造了一个现实──
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Because we actually created a reality where six months later,
Dialogue: 3,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我在北大西洋2.5英里水下 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I find myself in a Russian submersible
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,身处一个俄罗斯潜水器中 
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,two and a half miles down in the north Atlantic,
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,通过一个视口观望真正的泰坦尼克 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,looking at the real Titanic through a view port.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,不是电影 不是高清 而是身临其境 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Not a movie, not HD -- for real.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,那次经历令我大为惊叹 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Now, that blew my mind.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,前期的准备工作是很繁琐的 我们需要搭建摄像机 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it took a lot of preparation, we had to build cameras
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,灯光等等 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and lights and all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但真正让我震惊的是
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But, it struck me how much
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这些深海潜水活动
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,this dive, these deep dives,
Dialogue: 3,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,就如宇宙探险一样 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,was like a space mission.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,两者都是高科技产物 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You know, where it was highly technical,
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,两者都需要缜密的部署 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and it required enormous planning.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,你踏进船舱 踏入这漆黑
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You get in this capsule, you go down to this dark
Dialogue: 3,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,险恶的环境 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,hostile environment
Dialogue: 3,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,如果你无法依靠自己的力量返回的话 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,where there is no hope of rescue
Dialogue: 3,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,你是没有任何被营救的可能的 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,if you can't get back by yourself.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我当时想到 “天呀 我就好像
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I thought like, "Wow. I'm like,
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,活在一个科幻电影里面一样 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,living in a science fiction movie.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,太酷了！”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,This is really cool."
Dialogue: 3,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,正因此 深海探险成了我新的嗜好 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And so, I really got bitten by the bug of deep-ocean exploration.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,当然了 这归结于其中的好奇感 科学性 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Of course, the curiosity, the science component of it --
Dialogue: 3,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,它是万物合一 是探求未知 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,it was everything. It was adventure,
Dialogue: 3,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是好奇无边 是想象无限 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,it was curiosity, it was imagination.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:49.82,0:08:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是好莱坞无法给予我的难得经历  
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.82,0:08:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it was an experience that Hollywood couldn't give me. 
Dialogue: 3,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.53,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,虽然我可以想象出一个生物 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.53,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Because, you know, I could imagine a creature 
Dialogue: 3,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.85,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,然后利用电脑特效将它创造出来 
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.85,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and we could create a visual effect for it.  
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但我却无法想象出那天我透过潜水窗所看到的一切  
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't imagine what I was seeing out that window. 
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在我们随后的探险过程中 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,As we did some of our subsequent expeditions,
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我观测到过居住在热液喷口的生物 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I was seeing creatures at hydrothermal vents
Dialogue: 3,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,有时会看到我之前从来没有看过的东西 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and sometimes things that I had never seen before,
Dialogue: 3,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,有时会看到任何人之前都没有看过的东西 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,sometimes things that no one had seen before,
Dialogue: 3,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,甚至是一些在我们当时目击并记录之前
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that actually were not described by science
Dialogue: 3,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,还没有被科学所描述的事物 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,at the time that we saw them and imaged them.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,正因此 我对此是神魂颠倒 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, I was completely smitten by this,
Dialogue: 3,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,不得不继续下去 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and had to do more.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,于是我做出了一个令人惊讶的决定 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And so, I actually made a kind of curious decision.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在《泰坦尼克号》取得成功之后 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,After the success of "Titanic,"
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我决定 “好吧 我在好莱坞制作电影的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I said, "OK, I'm going to park my day job
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,到这里就可以告一段落了 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,as a Hollywood movie maker,
Dialogue: 3,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在接下来的一段时间里 我要成为一名全职探险家 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to go be a full-time explorer for a while."
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因此 我们开始计划
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And so, we started planning these
Dialogue: 3,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这些探险活动 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,expeditions.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们前往俾斯麦沉船 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And we wound up going to the Bismark,
Dialogue: 3,0:09:40.82,0:09:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,利用机器人装置来探测它的残骸 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.82,0:09:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and exploring it with robotic vehicles.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们随后又回到了泰坦尼克的残骸 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,We went back to the Titanic wreck.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,并且创造出了一批可以
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,We took little bots that we had created
Dialogue: 3,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,缠绕光学纤维的机器人 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that spooled a fiber optic.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,目的就是深入到残骸中 探索其内部的样子
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And the idea was to go in and do an interior
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,──一个前无古人的做法 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,survey of that ship, which had never been done.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.40,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在此之前 没有人看过残骸的内部 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.40,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Nobody had ever looked inside the wreck.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.75,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,他们没有所需要的技术 
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.75,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,They didn't have the means to do it, 
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以我们就创造出相应的技术  
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.80,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,so we created technology to do it. 
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,要知道 我当时就在泰坦尼克的甲板上 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, you know, here I am now, on the deck
Dialogue: 3,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,坐在一个潜水器内 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of Titanic, sitting in a submersible,
Dialogue: 3,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,看着就如同这个的木质甲板 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and looking out at planks that look much like this,
Dialogue: 3,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,心想着曾在这里表演的乐队 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,where I knew that the band had played.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我操控着一个小型的机器人探索器
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I'm flying a little robotic vehicle
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,飞过船内的走廊 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,through the corridor of the ship.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,虽然我在操控着它 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,When I say, "I'm operating it,"
Dialogue: 3,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我的思想却是在这个探索器内 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,but my mind is in the vehicle.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我感觉我确确实实地
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I felt like I was physically present
Dialogue: 3,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,置身在泰坦尼克的残骸中 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,inside the shipwreck of Titanic.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,那是我所经历过的最难以置信的
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it was the most surreal kind
Dialogue: 3,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,此曾相识的感觉 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of deja vu experience I've ever had,
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.82,0:10:35.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因为在机器人的探测灯照亮周围之前 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.82,0:10:35.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,because I would know before I turned a corner
Dialogue: 3,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我就已经知道每个转角背后
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,what was going to be there before the lights
Dialogue: 3,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所隐藏的一切 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of the vehicle actually revealed it,
Dialogue: 3,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,原因就在于电影制作的过程中 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,because I had walked the set for months
Dialogue: 3,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我花费了很多个月的时间在这个场景中走来走去 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,when we were making the movie.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而摄影棚中的道具就是依照这个船的设计图
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And the set was based as an exact replica
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所制造出来的一个真实模型 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,on the blueprints of the ship.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以那一次的经历是非比寻常的 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, it was this absolutely remarkable experience.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,它使我感受到了一种
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it really made me realize that
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,远程监控的经历──
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,the telepresence experience --
Dialogue: 3,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们甚至上拥有这些机器人形态的阿凡达 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that you actually can have these robotic avatars,
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.82,0:11:02.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们将我们的思想意识注入其中 
Dialogue: 2,0:10:57.82,0:11:02.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,then your consciousness is injected into the vehicle,
Dialogue: 3,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,注入另外一种存在形式中 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,into this other form of existence.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这的确是很深刻的感受 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,It was really, really quite profound.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,也许这一切可以让我们大致猜想几十年后的世界
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it may be a little bit of a glimpse as to what might be happening
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,会是怎样 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,some decades out
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,作为一名科学小说迷
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,as we start to have cyborg bodies
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我可以想象各种
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,for exploration or for other means
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,后人类社会的未来 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in many sort of
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,利用半机械人
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,post-human futures
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,来进行探险
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that I can imagine,
Dialogue: 3,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,以及其他活动 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,as a science fiction fan.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:24.82,0:11:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以通过这些探险
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.82,0:11:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, having done these expeditions,
Dialogue: 3,0:11:29.82,0:11:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我开始真正地欣赏海底的美妙 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.82,0:11:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and really beginning to appreciate what was down there,
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,比如那些生活在深海裂口处的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,such as at the deep ocean vents
Dialogue: 3,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,奇妙的动物们 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,where we had these amazing, amazing animals --
Dialogue: 3,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,它们算得上就是地球上的外星生物 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,they're basically aliens right here on Earth.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,它们住在一个化学合成的环境中 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,They live in an environment of chemosynthesis.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,完全不需要我们赖以生存的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,They don't survive on sunlight-based
Dialogue: 3,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,太阳光照 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,system the way we do.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以当你看到那些
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And so, you're seeing animals that are living next to
Dialogue: 3,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,生活在500度高温的海底地柱周边的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,a 500-degree-Centigrade
Dialogue: 3,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,动物的时候 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,water plumes.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,你觉得它们完全不可能存活 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You think they can't possibly exist.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,与此同时 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,At the same time
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我也开始对太空科技感兴趣 
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I was getting very interested in space science as well --
Dialogue: 3,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这自然也是受到了年少时候科学小说的影响 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,again, it's the science fiction influence, as a kid.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,结果我和太空社区建立了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I wound up getting involved with
Dialogue: 3,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,很紧密的联系 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,the space community,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,和美国航天局合作 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,really involved with NASA,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,成为了他们咨询委员会的一员 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,sitting on the NASA advisory board,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,策划真正的太空任务 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,planning actual space missions,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,前往俄罗斯 参观宇航员之前的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,going to Russia, going through the pre-cosmonaut
Dialogue: 3,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,生物科学协议
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,biomedical protocols,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,等等一系列的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and all these sorts of things,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,以便于我们带着我们的3D摄影器材
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,to actually go and fly to the international space station
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,前往国际空间站 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,with our 3D camera systems.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这种经历是令人难忘的 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And this was fascinating.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但我到头来所做的 却是说服太空科学家们
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.82,0:12:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But what I wound up doing was bringing space scientists
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,跟随我们前往海洋深处 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,with us into the deep.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,让他们可以切身体验 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And taking them down so that they had access --
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.82,0:12:38.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,太空生物学家 天体科学家
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.82,0:12:38.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,astrobiologists, planetary scientists,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,等等对极端环境感兴趣的人们
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,people who were interested in these extreme environments --
Dialogue: 3,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,都被我们带到深海裂口处 让他们能亲眼观看 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,taking them down to the vents, and letting them see,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,采取样品 探测仪器等等 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and take samples and test instruments, and so on.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以我们在制作记录片的同时
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, here we were making documentary films,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,却是在研究科学
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,but actually doing science,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,研究太空科学 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and actually doing space science.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我把小时候
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.82,0:12:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I'd completely closed the loop
Dialogue: 3,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,身为科学小说迷的经历
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,between being the science fiction fan,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,和真实从事这一行业的经历
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,you know, as a kid,
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,联系到了一起 
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and doing this stuff for real.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在这个探索之旅中 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And you know, along the way in this journey
Dialogue: 3,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,of discovery,
Dialogue: 3,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,学到了很多东西 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我学到了很多关于科学的东西 但我也学会了很多
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot about science. But I also learned a lot
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,关于领袖才能的东西 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,about leadership.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,你觉得导演必须得是一名领袖人才 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Now you think director has got to be a leader,
Dialogue: 3,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,是领导 是掌舵者之类的 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,leader of, captain of the ship, and all that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但在这些探险之前 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I didn't really learn about leadership
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我对领袖才能却是一无所知 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,until I did these expeditions.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因为我终究要问自己 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Because I had to, at a certain point, say,
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,“我到底在做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,"What am I doing out here?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我为什么要做这些事情？我从中得到什么呢？”
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Why am I doing this? What do I get out of it?"
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这些该死的纪录片根本不赚钱 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,We don't make money at these damn shows.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我们想回本都不容易 没名没份的 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,We barely break even. There is no fame in it.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,很多人都认为我在《泰坦尼克》和《阿凡达》两部电影之间
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,People sort of think I went away
Dialogue: 3,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,退居幕后 坐在沙滩上面
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,between "Titanic" and "Avatar" and was buffing my nails
Dialogue: 3,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,修指甲罢了 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,someplace, sitting at the beach.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但事实上我制作了这些电影 这些纪录片 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Made all these films, made all these documentary films
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,只有很少数的观众看过 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,for a very limited audience.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,没名 没份 没钱 你到底在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,No fame, no glory, no money. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我做这一切是为了这个经历本身的价值
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You're doing it for the task itself,
Dialogue: 3,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,为了这个挑战──
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,for the challenge --
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而大海就是最富挑战的环境 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and the ocean is the most challenging environment there is --
Dialogue: 3,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我做这一切也是为了探索发现的惊奇感 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,for the thrill of discovery,
Dialogue: 3,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,为了那种一小群人组成一个紧密的团队时
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and for that strange bond that happens
Dialogue: 3,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所撞击出的奇妙的凝聚力 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,when a small group of people form a tightly knit team.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,因为每一次我们都会和10到12个人
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Because we would do these things with 10, 12 people,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,一起工作上几个年头 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,working for years at a time,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,有时要在海上呆上个2-3个月 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,sometimes at sea for two, three months at a time.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:13.82,0:14:16.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而在那种凝聚力下 你意识到
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.82,0:14:16.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And in that bond, you realize
Dialogue: 3,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,最重要的事情
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that the most important thing
Dialogue: 3,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,就是你与他们
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,is the respect that you have for them
Dialogue: 3,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,彼此之间的尊敬 你们共同完成了一个
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and that they have for you, that you've done a task
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,无法向他人解释的任务 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that you can't explain to someone else.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,当你回到海岸上 你会说 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,When you come back to the shore and you say,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,“我们需要做这个 这个光学纤维 这个电律衰减 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,"We had to do this, and the fiber optic, and the attentuation,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,还有这个 那个 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and the this and the that,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,各项技术 其中的难度 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,all the technology of it, and the difficulty,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,海上作业的工作效率──
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,the human-performance aspects of working at sea,"
Dialogue: 3,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.08,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这些都是你无法向他人解释的 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.08,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,you can't explain it to people. 
Dialogue: 3,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.67,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这就好像那些同甘共苦过的 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.67,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,It's that thing that maybe cops have, or people in combat that  
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,警察 战士一样 他们知道
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,have gone through something together
Dialogue: 3,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,他们是无法向其他人解释其中的经历的 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and they know they can never explain it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,创造一个凝聚力 创造一个充满尊重之情的凝聚力 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Creates a bond, creates a bond of respect.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以当我回来制作我的下一部电影
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, when I came back to make my next movie,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,《阿凡达》的时候 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.82,0:14:51.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,which was "Avatar,"
Dialogue: 3,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我试着应用同样的领导信条──
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I tried to apply that same principle of leadership,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,尊敬你的团队 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,which is that you respect your team,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,他们才会回过头来尊敬你 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and you earn their respect in return.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而这一信条的确是改变了团队的活力 
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it really changed the dynamic.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.82,0:15:03.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我再次和一个小团队走到了一起
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.82,0:15:03.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, here I was again with a small team,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,共同前往未知的领域
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in uncharted territory,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,制作《阿凡达》 创造不曾存在过的
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,doing "Avatar," coming up with new technology
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,新科技 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that didn't exist before.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,振奋人心 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Tremendously exciting.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,充满挑战 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Tremendously challenging.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,在四年半的时间里 我们变成了一个大家庭 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And we became a family, over a four-and-half year period.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这个经历彻底改变了我制作电影的方式 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.82,0:15:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And it completely changed how I do movies.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,人们评论说 你把海底生物
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, people have commented on how, "Well, you know,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:20.82,0:15:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,带回到人们视野中来
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.82,0:15:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,you brought back the ocean organisms
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,放到了潘朵拉这个星球上 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and put them on the planet of Pandora."
Dialogue: 3,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,对于我而言 更侧重于做事的基本法则
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,To me, it was more of a fundamental way of doing business,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.01,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,和这个过程本身 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.01,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,the process itself,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,从而改变了事情的结果 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,, that changed as a result of that.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,所以我们从这一切中得到了什么呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,So, what can we synthesize out of all this?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,学到了哪些东西呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,You know, what are the lessons learned?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我觉得第一点就是
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Well, I think number one is
Dialogue: 3,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,好奇心 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,curiosity.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,这是你所拥有的最有力的东西 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,It's the most powerful thing you own.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,想象力是一种力量
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Imagination is a force
Dialogue: 3,0:15:46.82,0:15:50.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,一种可以反映现实的力量 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.82,0:15:50.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that can actually manifest a reality.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,而你团队对你的尊敬
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And the respect of your team
Dialogue: 3,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,要比这个世界上所有其他的桂冠
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,is more important than all the
Dialogue: 3,0:15:56.82,0:15:59.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,都要重要 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.82,0:15:59.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,laurels in the world.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,有时年轻电影导演
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,I have young filmmakers
Dialogue: 3,0:16:01.82,0:16:05.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,会问我 “给我一些电影方面的建议 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.82,0:16:05.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,come up to me and say, "Give me some advice for doing this."
Dialogue: 3,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,我的回答是 “不要局限你自己 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And I say, "Don't put limitations on yourself.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,别人会来局限你 会为你去划边界 但你不要自己局限自己 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,Other people will do that for you -- don't do it to yourself,
Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,不要赌自己会输 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,don't bet against yourself,
Dialogue: 3,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,要敢于冒险 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,and take risks."
Dialogue: 3,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,美国航空局有一则他们很喜欢的名言 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,NASA has this phrase that they like:
Dialogue: 3,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,“失败不是一个选项 ”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,"Failure is not an option."
Dialogue: 3,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,但在艺术和探险中 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,But failure has to be an option
Dialogue: 3,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,失败必定是个选项 因为这些都需要敢于挑战的信心 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,in art and in exploration, because it's a leap of faith.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,没有哪个需要创新的
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,And no important endeavor
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.82,YYeTS-CHS-480p,,0,0,0,,重要奋斗
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.82,YYeTS-ENG-480p,,0,0,0,,that required innovation
